   10. Project-Specific Descriptions for AstroChat AI
      AstroChat AI is a Telegram chat-bot and mini-application integrating
      AI dialogue, voice assistant, and content management. Key features:
      
      - Interactive live chat with humor, philosophical, and informative modes.
      - Random quote generation with rarity levels (common, rare, mythic).
      - Admin panel for managing users, channels, premium access, and content.
      - Integration with Google Play, App Store, and P2P payment systems.
      - AstroSecurity system: automatic scanning and self-healing of vulnerabilities.
      - Voice and text communication on multiple devices.
      - Premium features: advanced dialogues, interactive emoji, and media generation.
      - Compliance with privacy policies, restricted content handling, and user safety.
      - Scalable architecture with room for future extensions and additional modules.
      
      These descriptions serve as guidance for the scope and allowed use of AstroChat
      AI under this License.

